              <table id="EditorialReviewsPanel" class="ReviewSection" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"><tr><td>
	
                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">This tutorial guide provides information on how to design, debug, and deploy applications using component-based development and the new development tool from Visual Studio.NET -- Visual C#. Visual C# provides power and speed in an object-oriented environment so developers can create and deploy flexible applications quickly. The author also explains how to develop a wide variety of components, such as web controls, data access, enterprise level components, file service, multithreaded components, accessibility components, and more.</span>
              
</td></tr></table>
